n the system. The\ndepth and duration of the eclipse allow us to infer some of the properties of\nthe X-ray emitting region around that star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Mar 2003 00:42:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
